The paper deals with image classification using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep neural networks also falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper specifically deals with handwritten character recognition, which is a subfield of natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper also discusses the use of information retrieval techniques to improve classification accuracy, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR).
